|**OpenAI Researcher Access Program**|Potential direct API-credit path if the research framing is accepted.|Prepare as soon as the current research thesis / partner framing is tight enough.
|**Google for Nonprofits**|Workspace, ecosystem credibility, and adjacent benefits.|Apply now.
|**GitHub for Nonprofits**|Direct value for organization tooling; useful even before larger grant rounds.|Apply now.
